%description
This package implements a Kolmogorov Smirnov rank-sum based algorithm for
training (i.e. discriminant analysis--identification of genes that
discriminate between classes) and classification of gene expression data
sets.  One of the chief strengths of this approach is that it is amenable
to the "multiclass" problem. That is, it can discriminate between more
than 2 classes.

